comments: Beverley (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position during Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Favors (NOP) makes contact with the ball and cleanly deflects Leonard's (LAC) pass attempt at the end of his drive.
Harrell (LAC) makes incidental leg to ball contact during the loose ball.
Shamet (LAC) commits a take foul on Hart (NOP).
After absorbing the contact, Leonard (LAC) briefly places two hands on the opposite side of Redick's (NOP) body but he immediately removes his hands. The contact is marginal.
Favors (NOP) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Shamet's (LAC) path and he is firming up when the contact occurs during the pick.
Leonard (LAC) slightly extends his forearm into Ball's (NOP) front as both player move in the same direction during the drive. Ball's (NOP) momentum carries him away from the marginal contact.
Favors (NOP) is in the paint and actively guarding an opponent within three seconds.
Ball (NOP) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Leonard (LAC) after the release of the ball during his jump shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position during Williams' (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Favors (NOP) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Shamet's (LAC) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the screen.
Ball (NOP) makes marginal foot to foot contact in Leonard's (LAC) landing area following his jump shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) briefly grasps Beverley's (LAC) jersey during the rebound. The contact is marginal.
Shamet (LAC) and Ingram (NOP) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Leonard (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position during Redick's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
